      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented release notes and regression test suite.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R2 employed under institutional software quality plan. Version control, change logs, and automated regression tests for hemolysis scalar transport confirmed. Achieved level meets required level for MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver verified against at least one canonical benchmark with documented convergence behavior.",
      "rationale": "Solver verified against the FDA nozzle benchmark (ASME V&V 20 dataset). Second-order spatial convergence confirmed for velocity and scalar transport. Residual convergence to 1e-6 enforced for all simulations."
    },
    {
